Careful Observation<tab><var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Specialist Action<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>

Do nothing for one step, preserving the status of any actions presently in effect.

A crafter's delineation is used upon execution.
Can only be used up to three times per synthesis.
This action does not increase step count.

Heart and Soul<tab><var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Specialist Action<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>

Allows the execution of <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Precise Touch<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Intensive Synthesis<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>, or <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Tricks of the Trade<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> regardless of material condition.
Effect ends if the aforementioned actions are executed when material condition is not <var 48 F201FA /var><var 49 F201FB /var>Good<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> or <var 48 F201FA /var><var 49 F201FB /var>Excellent<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var>.

A crafter's delineation is used upon execution.
Can only be used once per synthesis.
This action does not increase step count.

Wird eines dieser Kommandos während <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Gut<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> oder <var 48 F201F4 /var><var 49 F201F5 /var>Exzellent<var 49 01 /var><var 48 01 /var> eingesetzt, endet der Effekt.
